<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Tips</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>Screen 01: Dead simple
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 02: Knock beacons off then kill ring before other balls
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 03: Get P then bong aliens while in centre of the screen
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 04: Get jump then bump spider, stay near centre of the screen and kill
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 05: Get jump to high, then grab jump and P, then bump
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 06: Get P, then bonus, then ring
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 07: Power 3/4 of max, get P
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 08: Power 3/4 of max, get P by jumping, bonus then jump
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 09: Power 3/4 of max. Stay near centre, just keep going
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 10: Collect bonus, if any, then the P, kill
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 11: Power 1/3 then bump away
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 12: Power 1/2, no jump, bump
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 13: Power 1/2, no jump, collect jump
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 14: Power 1/2, collect every symbol
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 15: Low power, only collect if desperate
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 16: 1/2 power, preserve!
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 17: Full except 2, easy
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 18: 1 power point, bonus
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 19: Get bonus, power high
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Screen 20: No P, get P's
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Lives</td><td>42241,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Energy</td><td>42462,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Jumps</td><td>42473,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lives = x</td><td>33300,x (x= 1-255)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Start Same Level</td><td>33288,0</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR><B><U>A couple of points about the "Start Same Level" POKE</U>
<UL>
<LI>It's only really useful if you aren't using Infinite Lives as it restarts you on
the level you died on, instead of back to level 1.
<LI>Because of the way the POKE works, you have to have a normal game BEFORE using
the POKE, as the variables aren't set up at first, and it tries to start the game
on level 0, and crashes.
</UL>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
